data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Lithonia, Georgia! This charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath with an additional bonus room is strategically situated less than 7 miles from the The Mall at Stoonecrest & Arabia Mountain. Offering convenience for frequent travelers & boasting a cozy family room adorned with a classic fireplace this home will provide lots of warmth and comfort. Its prime location ensures easy access to an array of shops, restaurants, and stores, making errands and leisure activities a breeze. Nestled in a quiet and friendly community, this property provides the perfect blend of tranquility and accessibility, creating an ideal haven for you and your loved ones. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Lithonia gem your new home! 1 year home warranty included!
